M9
M5
L M140 MB MAX
L X+1.968504 Y+1.968504 R0 FMAX M91
M30

LBL 100 ;2D-Face (7)
L Z+0.19685 FMAX
L Z-0.04 FQ57
L X-3.189606 FQ52
CC X-3.189606 Y-0.45628
CP IPA-180 DR- FQ59
L X+3.189606 Y+0.062441 FQ52
L Z+0.590551 FMAX
